(3346, 25, '2017-02-17 14:27:14', '2017-02-17 14:27:14', '<p>[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Default%20Bearer%20is%20a%20term%20arose%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20Evolved%20Packet%20Core%20and%20LTE.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EIt%20represnts%20the%20EPS%20bearer%20which%20is%20first%20established%20for%20a%20new%20PDN%20connection%20and%20remains%20established%20throughout%20the%20lifetime%20of%20the%20PDN%20connection.\",\"rhsI\":\"Dedicated%26nbsp%3BBearer%20is%20a%20term%20arose%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20Evolved%20Packet%20Core%20and%20got%20more%20fame%20with%20the%20VoLTE%20commercial%20deployments.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EIt%20represents%20a%20context%20that%20is%20always%20linked%20to%20a%20default%20EPS%20bearer%20context%20and%20represents%20additional%20EPS%20bearer%20resources%20between%20the%20UE%20and%20the%20PDN.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Bitrate\",\"lhsI\":\"Default%20Bearer%20is%20characterized%20by%20Non-GBR%20%28Non%20Guaranteed%20Bitrate%29.\",\"rhsI\":\"Dedicated%20Bearer%20Can%20be%20either%20GBR%20%28Guaranteed%20Bitrate%29%20or%20Non-GBR%26nbsp%3B%28Non%20Guaranteed%20Bitrate%29.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EThough%26nbsp%3Bthe%20GBR%20case%20is%20the%20most%20commercial%20deployed%20use%20case.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Use Case\",\"lhsI\":\"Default%20Bearer%20is%20commonly%20used%20for%20Internet%20Browsing%20and%20all%20Mobile%20Broadband%20services%20that%20don%27t%20require%20specific%20Quality%20of%20Service%20requirements.\",\"rhsI\":\"Dedicated%20Bearer%20is%20commonly%20used%20for%20Voice%20over%20LTE%20%28VoLTE%29%20and%20in%20theory%20to%20any%20service%20that%20require%20specific%20Quality%20of%20Service%20requirements.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Analogy to GPRS\",\"lhsI\":\"Default%20EPS%20Bearer%20can%20be%20analogised%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20Primary%26nbsp%3BPDP%20Context%20in%20PS%20Core/GPRS.\",\"rhsI\":\"Dedicated%26nbsp%3BEPS%20Bearer%20can%20be%20analogised%20to%20the%20concept