(3357, 34, '2017-02-18 15:48:22', '2017-02-18 15:48:22', '[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"A%20personality%20trait%20is%20a%20characteristic%20that%20is%20distinct%20to%20an%20individual.%20it%20is%26nbsp%3Bsimply%20the%20actions%2C%20attitudes%20and%20behaviors%20you%20possess.\",\"rhsI\":\"Personality%20disorders%20form%20a%20class%20of%20mental%20disorders%20that%20are%20characterized%20by%20long-lasting%2C%20rigid%20patterns%20of%20thought%20and%20behavior.%20While%20most%20people%20recognize%20traits%20of%20themselves%20in%20many%20different%20personality%20disorders%2C%20a%20person%20who%20qualifies%20for%20a%20personality%20disorder%20diagnosis%20will%20exhibit%20most%20such%20traits%20of%20a%20disorder.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Types\",\"lhsI\":\"There%20are%20so%20many%20types%20of%20personality%20traits%26nbsp%3Band%20it%20is%20sometimes%20difficult%20to%20classify%20a%20person%20into%20a%20single%20type%20as%20there%20are%20many%20different%20personality%20traits%20one%26nbsp%3Bcan%20possess.%3Cbr%20/%3E\",\"rhsI\":\"There%20are%2010%20major%20personality%20disorders%20which%20are%20grouped%20into%20three%20categories%3A%3Cbr%20/%3E1-%20Suspicious%3A%20paranoid%2C%20schizoid%2C%26nbsp%3Bschizotypal%20and%20antisocial.%3Cbr%20/%3E2-%20Emotional%20and%20impulsive%3A%20borderline%2C%20histrionic%20and%20%26nbsp%3Bnarcissistic.%3Cbr%20/%3E3-%20Anxious%3A%26nbsp%3Bavoidant%2C%26nbsp%3Bdependent%20and%26nbsp%3Bobsessive%20compulsive%3Cbr%20/%3E%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%3Cbr%20/%3E%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%3Cbr%20/%3E%26nbsp%3B%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E\"}]', 'Answer for What is the difference between Personality Traits &amp; Personality Disorders?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-personality-traits-personality-disorders', '', '', '2017-02-18 15:48:22', '2017-02-18 15:48:22', '', 3351, 'http://localhost/wp/dwqa-answer/answer-for-what-is-the-difference