(3378, 42, '2017-02-20 20:49:41', '2017-02-20 20:49:41', '[{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"The%20NAS%20node%20selection%20function%20%28NNSF%29%20enables%20the%20selection%20of%20a%20serving%20MSC%20for%20the%20MS.%20%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20entity%20that%20has%20the%20NNSF%20function%20is%20called%20an%20NNSF%20entity.%20%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20NNSF%20entity%20for%20this%20case%20is%20the%20MGW.%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20MGW%20should%20be%26nbsp%3Bconnected%20to%20multiple%20MSCs%20in%20the%20MSC%20Pool.%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20RAN%20node%20uses%20the%20SPC%20of%20the%20MGW%20%26nbsp%3Bto%20communicate%20with%20the%20MSCs.%20The%20SPC%20of%20MSCs%20are%20not%20available%20for%26nbsp%3BRAN%20nodes.\",\"rhsI\":\"The%20NAS%20node%20selection%20function%20%28NNSF%29%20enables%20the%20selection%20of%20a%20serving%20MSC%20for%20the%20MS.%20%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20entity%20that%20has%20the%20NNSF%20function%20is%20called%20an%20NNSF%20entity.%20%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20NNSF%20entity%20for%20this%20case%20is%20the%20BSC/RNC%20for%202G/3G%20respectively.%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20BSC/RNC%20should%20be%20connected%20to%20multiple%20MSCs%20in%20the%20MSC%20Pool.%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20RAN%20node%20uses%20the%20SPC%20of%20the%20MSC%26nbsp%3Bto%20communicate%20with%20it.%20The%20MGW%20serves%20as%20a%20signaling%20GW.%3Cbr%20/%3E\"}]', 'Answer for What is the difference between Implementing NNSF at MGW side &amp; Implementing NNSF at RAN side (Iu/A-Flex)?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-implementing-nnsf-at-mgw-side-implementing-nnsf-at-ran-side-iua-flex', '', '', '2017-02-20 20:49:41', '2017-02-20 20:49:41', '', 3361, 'http://localhost/wp/dwqa-answer/answer-for-what-is-the-difference-between-implementing-nnsf-at-mgw-side-implementing-nnsf-at-ran-side-iua-flex/', 0, 'dwqa-answer', '', 0),
(3379, 22, '2017-02-21 04:11:06', '2017-02-21 04:11:06', '<p>[{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Introduction\",\"lhsI\":\"Private%20Cloud%20and%20Public%20Cloud%20represent%20two%20different%20Deployment%20Models%20of%20Cloud%20Computing%20according%20to%20NIST%20%28National%20Institute%20of%20Standards%20and%20Technology%29%20definition.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EThere%20are%20two%20other%20deployment%20models%20explained%20by%20NIST%20in%20the%20same%20publication%3B%20namely%2C%20Community%20Cloud%20and%20Hybrid%20Cloud.\",\"rhsI\":\"\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"The%20cloud%20infrastructure%20is%20provisioned%20for%20open%20use%20by%20the%20general%20public.%20It%20may%20be%20owned%2C%20managed%2C%20and%20operated%20by%20a%20business%2C%20academic%2C%20or%20government%20organization%2C%20or%20some%20combination%20of%20them.%20It%20exists%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20cloud%20provider.\",\"rhsI\":\"The%20cloud%20infrastructure%20is%20provisioned%20for%20exclusive%20use%20by%20a%20single%20organization%20comprising%20multiple%20consumers%20%28e.g.%2C%20business%20units%29.%20It%20may%20be%20owned%2C%20managed%2C%20and%20operated%20by%20the%20organization%2C%20a%20third%20party%2C%20or%20some%20combination%20of%20them%2C%20and%20it%20may%20exist%20on%20or%20off%20premises.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"Examples\",\"lhsI\":\"Example%20of%20mega%20scale%20Public%20Cloud%20service%20providers%20are%3A%3Cbr%20/%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A//aws.amazon.com/%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3EAmazon%20Web%20Services%20%28AWS%29%3C/span%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/a%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A//cloud.google.com/%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%22%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-size%3A%2012.8px%3B%22%3EGoogle%20Cloud%20Platform%3C/span%3E%3C/span%3E%3C/