(3454, 34, '2017-03-02 07:51:29', '2017-03-02 07:51:29', '[{\"cellsNumber\":1,\"row\":\"Definition\",\"lhsI\":\"Blood%20pressure%20means%20the%20pressure%20of%20blood%20in%20your%20arteries%20as%20it%20is%20being%20pumped%20by%20the%20heart.%3Cbr%20/%3EBlood%20pressure%20is%20measured%20in%20millimetres%20of%20mercury.%20Normal%20blood%20pressure%26nbsp%3B%20as%20two%20figures%2C%20for%20example%20120/80%20mmHg.%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20first%20number%20%28120%26nbsp%3Bin%20this%20case%29%20is%20known%20as%26nbsp%3Bsystolic%20pressure%26nbsp%3B-%20pressure%20in%20the%20arteries%20when%20the%20heart%20contracts.%3Cbr%20/%3EThe%20second%20number%20%2880%29%20is%26nbsp%3Bdiastolic%20pressure%26nbsp%3B-%20the%20pressure%20in%20the%20arteries%20when%20the%20heart%20rests.%3Cbr%20/%3EIdeally%2C%20we%20should%20all%20have%20a%20blood%20pressure%20below%20120%20over%2080%20%28120/80%29.\",\"rhsI\":\"\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"what does it mean?\",\"lhsI\":\"High%20blood%20pressure%20occurs%26nbsp%3Bif%20the%20blood%20pressure%20readings%20are%20consistently%20140/90%20mmHg%2C%20or%20higher%2C%20over%20a%20number%20of%20weeks.%3Cbr%20/%3E\",\"rhsI\":\"A%20low%20blood%20pressure%20reading%20is%20having%20a%20level%20that%20is%2090/60mmHg%2C%20or%20lower.\"},{\"cellsNumber\":2,\"row\":\"How does if feel like?\",\"lhsI\":\"Usually%20no%20symptoms%20or%20complains%20unless%20very%20high%2C%20it%20may%20causes%3A%3Cbr%20/%3E%3Cbr%20/%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3EHeadaches%3C/span%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3EVision%20problems%3C/span%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3ENose%20bleeds%3C/span%3E%3C/li%3E%0A%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%20Lato%2C%20sans-serif%3B%20font-size%3A%200.8em%3B%22%3ETrouble%20breathin